# prefix-block-missing-value-inner

## Input

```
s. {
  lonely
  b 2
}

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..22
  PREFIX_BLOCK@0..22
    WORD_KEY@0..2
      WORD@0..2 "s."
    SPACE@2..3 " "
    OPEN_BRACE@3..4 "{"
    NEWLINE@4..5 "\n"
    SPACE@5..7 "  "
    ENTRY@7..13
      WORD_KEY@7..13
        WORD@7..13 "lonely"
    NEWLINE@13..14 "\n"
    SPACE@14..16 "  "
    ENTRY@16..20
      WORD_KEY@16..17
        WORD@16..17 "b"
      SPACE@17..18 " "
      INTEGER@18..19
        NUMERAL@18..19 "2"
      NEWLINE@19..20 "\n"
    CLOSE_BRACE@20..21 "}"
    NEWLINE@21..22 "\n"
```

## Syntax Error

```
[
    SyntaxError {
        message: "missing value for the key",
        range: 13..13,
    },
]
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        PrefixBlock {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..2 "s.",
            },
            open_brace: OPEN_BRACE@3..4 "{",
            items: [
                Entry {
                    key: WordKey {
                        word: WORD@7..13 "lonely",
                    },
                    value: none,
                },
                Entry {
                    key: WordKey {
                        word: WORD@16..17 "b",
                    },
                    value: Integer {
                        sign: none,
                        numeral: NUMERAL@18..19 "2",
                    },
                },
            ],
            close_brace: CLOSE_BRACE@20..21 "}",
        },
    ],
}
```

